txt.en: You have brought the Hobbits of the Company a great gift from your journeys through Mordor.
Hobbits of the Company: Gathering Rations
The Hobbits of the Company in Gondor seek rations from Mordor.
Bring the rations to the hobbits' guest-hall, near Cormallen
The Hobbits of the Company in Gondor seek rations from Mordor.
A collection box can be found in the hobbits' guest-hall, near Cormallen.\n\nBring the rations to the hobbits' guest-hall.
